aa(lp32
VNow, a hallmark of computer programs
p33
aVis just this kind of sensitivity to small changes.
p34
aVIf your bank account's one dollar, and you flip a single bit,
p35
aVyou could end up with a thousand dollars.
p36
aVSo these small changes are things that I think
p37
aVthat \u2014 they indicate to us that a complicated computation
p38
aVin development is underlying these amplified, large changes.
