aa(lp215
VNow, what's great about this is anybody can do this.
p216
aVAnd so, I got this in the mail about a year after I did this, unsolicited.
p217
aVAnyone know what this is? What is it?
p218
aVIt's China, right?
p219
aVSo, what happened is, a graduate student in China,
p220
aVLulu Qian, did a great job.
p221
aVShe wrote all her own software
p222
aVto design and built this DNA origami,
p223
aVa beautiful rendition of China, which even has Taiwan,
p224
aVand you can see it's sort of on the world's shortest leash, right?
p225
aV(Laughter)
p226
aVSo, this works really well
p227
aVand you can make patterns as well as shapes, OK?
p228
aVAnd you can make a map of the Americas and spell DNA with DNA.
